subject: Diving (Sports Event)
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Laura Wilkinson earned her third trip to the Olympics, holding off 15-year-old Haley Ishimatsu on the 10-meter platform Sunday at the United States diving trials in Indianapolis. Wilkinson, 30, who won the gold medal on platform at the 2000 Sydney Olympics, botched her second dive, but her next one produced all 10s.
